org.catacomb.numeric.difnet

Interface StructureNode

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BasicStructureNode

    public interface StructureNode
    properties of a node in a diffusible network. The corresponding node may containing multiple diffusible quantities, in which case the dq argument specifiew which to consult. NB, as yet dq is unsupported MISSING hasFixedValue should return true for nodes whosse value can't be changed, like an isopotential bath. In this case setValue does nothing and the result of getCapacitance is undefined. Such odes are important in a DiffusibleNet to break loops and take advantage of sparse matrix methods in computing the diffusion.
